## 🔘 UI Components: Button & Card Design

### Button Style

| Element      | Spec |
|--------------|------|
| **Base Color** | Secondary (Asparagus) |
| **Corner Radius** | 2px–4px |
| **Padding**      | `8px 12px` |
| **Border**      | Boxed 2px wide border |
| **Font**         | Pixelify Sans (uppercase) |
| **Outline**      | 1px darker asparagus or soft shadow (for depth) |
| **Hover**        | Slight increase in brightness + accent border (`#E63946`) |
| **Click**        | Shrinks 1px on all sides (bounce), fires ripple or glow animation |

> Animations are pixelated (no anti-aliasing), ~6fps, usually 4–6 frames long.

### Card Style

| Element         | Spec |
|-----------------|------|
| **Background**  | Timberwolf (`#CCC6BD`) |
| **Border**      | Boxed 2px wide border with Inner inset shadow using deep timberwolf |
| **Padding**     | 12px internal |
| **Elevation**   | Slight 1px "lift" using a darker pixel layer underneath |
| **Header Strip** | Optional top bar in accent red (`#E63946`) for category |


> Cards often serve as containers for info, pokédex-like data, or menu choices.

