## 🔠 Typography System

Typography mixes retro aesthetics with modern clarity.

| Use Case         | Font                         | Size Range | Notes |
|------------------|------------------------------|------------|-------|
| **Header / Title** | [**Press Start 2P**](mdc:https:/fonts.google.com/specimen/Press+Start+2P) | 16px–24px | Pixel-font caps for menu titles, location names |
| **Body Text**     |  | @**VT323** | Readable at small sizes, round edges, excellent for dialogue |
| **Buttons/Labels**| Tight 8px pixel fonts or bold uppercase Pixelify Sans | 8px–10px | Use for clear CTAs, toggles, tags |

### Textbox Styling Tips:
- Rounded corners, soft border (deep timberwolf)
- Fixed-width text wrapping (around 200–240px)
- Sound-style bounce or flicker on letter-by-letter reveal (à la Pokémon)

